icance lies in advancing generative AI beyond surface-level style transfer toward cognitively aware, pragmatically intelligent writing assistance. Potential applications include automated storytelling, educational writing tools, and adaptive content generation for diverse audiences. Moreover, this work contributes methodologically by formalizing figurative language integration as a sequential decision problem under uncertainty, opening new directions in controllable and interpretable NLG.",
